Package: mediaspin
Title: Annotation Pipeline for Media Bias Detection in News Headline Edits
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Preetika", "Verma", role = c("aut")),
    person("Kokil", "Jaidka", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "kokil.jaidka@gmail.com")
  )
Description: Provides an annotation pipeline for detecting 13 types of media bias
    in news headline edits. Uses the OpenAI API to analyze word-level changes
    between original and edited headlines, identifying bias patterns such as spin,
    sensationalism, omission, and more.
